org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.components.transformation.sync

Class CompTypeSync

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.components.transformation.sync.CompTypeSync

  • public class CompTypeSync
extends Object
    Create a UML like executor, i.e. for each port p with a provided interface I, add a get_p to the executor for each port q with a required interface I, add an attribute q to the executor. This attribute is manipulated by the container.
    Author:
    ansgar
